<title>ạ̉nạ bạlḥb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉nạ bạlḥb ạ̹dytk frḥ wkẖyr wslạm
 wjạy tqwlly nsytk wạ̉nạ ḥạrsk mạ bnạm)2
 1-(jạyz ạ̉smḥ bạltjrbh mrẗ jạyz ṭʿm ạltjrbh mrh
 lkn ʿmry mạ sbtk mrh dạymạaⁿ knt mʿạk
 knt bsẖwf ạ̹ymạnk by mḥtạj ạ̉smʿ ṣwtk ly
 wlw dqqt yạbny sẖwyh htlạqyny wyạk)2
 2-(ʿmạl tsẖky lyl wnhạr ạ̹ny ạ̉nạ sạybk bạ̹stmrạr
 wạ̹n ḥyạtk dy̱ ậtwn nạr wậlạmk btzyd
 wnạsy ạ̹n ktyr ʿlsẖạnk bzrʿ frḥ mkạn ạ̉ḥznk
 wạ̹ny ạ̉kẖdt yạ ạ̹bny mkạnk ạ̹zạy tbqy̱ wḥyd)2</lyrics>
